name: World Summit on Data Science and Machine Learning
content: Data science conferences, we invite all the honorable speakers, delegates, exhibitor, sponsors, researchers, experts, experimenters, officials, moderators, experimenter and students to join the data science congress 2022 on science and machine learning which will be conducted on August 08-09, 2022 Dublin, Ireland. The event welcomes all researchers to take bit in this conference on data science and machine learning. This conference is to get you strengths with the knowledge on data science to reach your goals.
